<br>
1)  Survival.  The ability to outrun most mobs out there, even in indoor zones will save you numerous times.  I imagine I've saved an AAs worth of exp already from being able to run for it... especially when soloing.  Also, it's even useful for druids and rangers and such... try zoning out of Tower of Frozen Shadows, and you'll get the idea... Sow would be interupted, but Run 3 is already engaged.<br>
<br>
2)  Convenience.  It lets me get places faster... even though I own JBoots, sometimes you need to do a long indoor run (Shadowhaven-Echo Caverns-Fungus Grove for example) and Run-3 helps a ton there.<br>
<br>
3)  CR.  This is more a rogue thing, but when you're sneaking about invis, you can't cast your boots even outside.  Run3 helps a lot here, since it means you can move as fast as the mobs even when sneak hiding and thus dodge see invis types.<br>
<br>
4) Pulling.  You run faster than the mobs you fight.  Thus, you don't get creamed while pulling.<br>
<br>
Now how many AAs come close to that?  First aid will help for soloing warriors rogues and monks, but run speed can help just as much there in terms of pulling the mobs back to where you wish to fight them and ensuring survival.  Regen is very nice in guild raid situations, and lowers downtime a bit when soloing, but in the soloing situation the ability to outrun mobs may lower downtime just as much.  6 stamina for 3 AA ain't that much... by the time you're 50+, we can assume you're above 100 stamina, so it's just raw hitpoints... useful to a tank, but still, not as helpful as Runspeed, and you get more HPs by leveling anyway.<br>
<br>
So yeah, runspeed is basically rocks.<br>
<br>
Jarkell Ravensteel <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=dalninil@firionavie>Dalninil</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 602<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(11/3/02 2:57 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm43.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=153.topic&index=37>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: For the general regen AA ..</span><hr size=1> Why I went run 3<br>
